>> time required: 2 hours
>> course: main

Make marinade, mix @brown sugar{1%cup}, @soy sauce{1%cup}, minced @garlic cloves{3}, minced @ginger{3%cm}
Slice @pork butt{1%kg} into 5cm pieces
Marinate ~{24%hours}
Heat smoker to 95°C
Smoke ~{4%hours} or until internal temp is 63°C
Remove from smoker, slice into bite sizes and fry with @guava jelly{2%tbsp} and sliced @sweet onion{1}